title: Walter Feichter
text: Walter Feichter (born 1 April 1974) is an Italian <a href="snowboarding">snowboarder</a>. He competed in the <a href="Snowboarding%20at%20the%202002%20Winter%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Men%27s%20parallel%20giant%20slalom">men's parallel giant slalom event</a> at the <a href="2002%20Winter%20Olympics">2002 Winter Olympics</a>.
